The '''White Dragon''', known as the '''Frost D''' in the [[Nintendo Entertainment System]] version, is an enemy in the original ''[[Final Fantasy]]''. White Dragon appears later in the [[Chaos Shrine (Final Fantasy)|Chaos Shrine]], on the first floor. The dragon appears also in the [[Lifespring Grotto]], in a room where a dragon, [[Bahamut (Final Fantasy)|Dark Bahamut]], orders the party to kill some of its disciples to continue to the next level. One of the disciples may be the White Dragon, which the party can fight. They sometimes come in groups of up to four dragons.

