== Battle ==
White Dragons are not as difficult to defeat as the [[Red Dragon (Final Fantasy)|Red Dragon]], having less [[HP (stat)|HP]], Attack, and stats overall; which is strange, because the party is supposed to visit the [[Cavern of Ice]] after the visit to [[Mount Gulg (Final Fantasy)|Mount Gulg]]. The White Dragon is of the [[Ice (Final Fantasy)|ice]] element, and thus is weak to [[Fire (Final Fantasy element)|fire]] attacks, and resists ice attacks. The dragon is also weak to [[Lightning (Final Fantasy)|lightning]]. As with many winged enemies, the dragon is immune to [[Earth (Final Fantasy)|earth-element]] attacks, and it is also invulnerable to [[Poison (Final Fantasy)|poison]] and [[Stone (Final Fantasy)|stone]].

Even if the White Dragon is weaker than its red counterpart, it still has a trick up its sleeve: Icestorm, which deals ice damage to all [[party]] members, and can be dangerous for members with low [[Magic Defense (stat)|magic defense]].

=== Strategy ===
A single [[Firaga (ability)|Firaga]] will either finish it off or leave it very weak.

